# Optional: force API calls to another origin (cross-origin; needs CORS on the API).
# Leave unset on Vercel so the app uses same-origin /api → vercel.json rewrite (no CORS preflight).
# Ignored during `npm run dev` — local uses /api → Vite proxy → http://localhost:4000
# VITE_API_URL=https://example-api.vercel.app
